Package burlap.behavior.singleagent.vfa.cmac

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AttributeTileSpecification
    Specifies how a single attribute of a specific object class is to be tiled.
    CMACFeatureDatabase
    A feature database using CMACs [1] AKA Tiling Coding over OO-MDP states.
    FVCMACFeatureDatabase
    A feature database using CMACs [1] AKA Tiling Coding for states that are first converted into a feature vector.
    FVTiling
    This class provides a tiling of a provided feature vector.
    Tiling
    This class provides a tiling specification, which tiles a state according to multi-dimensional tiling of specified attributes for specified object classes.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    CMACFeatureDatabase.TilingArrangement
    Enum for specifying whether tilings should have their tile alignments should be chossen so that they are randomly jittered from each other, or if each subsequent tiling should be offset by a uniform amount.
